  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Humanitarian innovation and evidence programme: improved analysis of disaster risk and increased capacity to deliver humanitarian assistance</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This is one of three business cases which implements the DFID Humanitarian Innovation and Evidence Strategy. This programme will commission research which will make it easier for decision-makers to use risk analysis; improve understanding of risk in urban areas; improve disaster risk modelling and analysis; establish the most effective ways to deliver aid in insecure environments; and identify ways to strengthen national and local capacity to respond to disasters.</narrative>
  </description>
